    "description": "🐤Steam历史上最充满爱的、<strong>以生存者为基础的射击游戏</strong>来了!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271940/extras/f401ba787f66eb4dcb297b0378ed11b6.poster.avif?t=1740819080\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271940/extras/f401ba787f66eb4dcb297b0378ed11b6.webm?t=1740819080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271940/extras/f401ba787f66eb4dcb297b0378ed11b6.mp4?t=1740819080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br>🤗这个游戏的目的是要<strong>拥抱和捆绑</strong>这个叛逆的小可爱!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271940/extras/19a4cedea8937b37ba25f7d0d33f3bb8.poster.avif?t=1740819080\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271940/extras/19a4cedea8937b37ba25f7d0d33f3bb8.webm?t=1740819080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271940/extras/19a4cedea8937b37ba25f7d0d33f3bb8.mp4?t=1740819080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br>🍅英雄没有战斗能力。 但他可以<strong>拥抱</strong>和爱他的朋友！！！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271940/extras/a61c502f3cb6d0720051b56ed431afcc.poster.avif?t=1740819080\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271940/extras/a61c502f3cb6d0720051b56ed431afcc.webm?t=1740819080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271940/extras/a61c502f3cb6d0720051b56ed431afcc.mp4?t=1740819080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>🍔拥抱这两个可爱的盟友，他们会<strong>发射子弹</strong>! 一个可靠的伙伴......！！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271940/extras/433e972a1722542baa9ab45368c7affb.poster.avif?t=1740819080\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271940/extras/433e972a1722542baa9ab45368c7affb.webm?t=1740819080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271940/extras/433e972a1722542baa9ab45368c7affb.mp4?t=1740819080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br>🧬不要忘了<strong>升级</strong>! 大力加强！！！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271940/extras/84f04c8f6b6c3bed651fad59ecb759d9.poster.avif?t=1740819080\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271940/extras/84f04c8f6b6c3bed651fad59ecb759d9.webm?t=1740819080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271940/extras/84f04c8f6b6c3bed651fad59ecb759d9.mp4?t=1740819080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br>🍧即使有强大的敌人袭击，三个人的爱情也是不可战胜的。 让我们继续努力，<strong>hugsurvivor!!! </strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271940/extras/e36d7d53245f9bcb6df9b358b61c6d5c.avif?t=1740819080\" width=600 height=100 /></span>",
